Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 綯 別理這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 岡倫也有份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴小姐早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說我說 後來怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間機器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問過約翰‧提托了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過我開始搞不懂那傢伙說的是否正確了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一塊啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼這麼激動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是個提托宅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 克莉絲醬 嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 又擦出火花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架很讓人難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止私人性質的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是那種能簡單判斷出過去是否改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天之前我換了手機的機型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想告訴自己還是不換比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果過去改變了 桐生小姐的手機也會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一目瞭然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 實驗開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 電話烤箱（暫定） 啟動…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好圓呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岡…凶真先生托我買的樂透6 我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…心意很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離你睜開心眼的日子也不遠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 那麼我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好像也挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次會來穿真由喜的Cos吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我對這些東西還是有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得會很合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是…這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去…改變了？
