Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃光的指壓師在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shi…啊？
