Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用日語就OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華子他…沒來過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華君？ 沒來過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那萌郁呢 萌郁怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萌郁？ 那是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐生萌郁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天沒來嗎 到底有沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐生萌郁？ 我也沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你又用D-MAIL了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 等…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去發生了改變 使萌郁整個人都消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收信記錄裡直到7月31號前 萌郁的簡訊記錄都還留著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:39.43,tip,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz6\fs43\bord0\be1\pos(757,237)}我是萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會再發簡訊給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 在四天前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了簡訊的桐生…萌郁小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的行動發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導致過去變成了她沒有來Lab的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 這次也只有你一人記得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…Reading Steiner來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提 你這個造詞太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得還是不要用了比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的個人見解是不必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越世界線也能保留記憶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岡倫 明天見～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份力量是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.11,tip,NTP,0,0,0,,字：希望你能成為救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那些人居然能在Lab過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說這樣才算是科學狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 下次大家一起來過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要男生就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 要不要來我住的旅館？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那下次我就去打擾你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華君 嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然沒帶妖刀五月雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦 岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華君今天可是真由喜的客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是來穿真由喜的COS服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來來 琉華君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來變身吧 變身變身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 脫掉脫掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要碰那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了 我自己穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 不要碰那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要穿這個可是有訣竅的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 別脫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常…百合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 琉華子是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不要臉了
