Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岡倫你覺得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在正遭受著強烈的精神衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 內心…內心要被侵蝕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了 凶真先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又在鬧什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉絲醬 嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼從頭到腳打量人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 毫無羞恥的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 這個COS服 適合琉華君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很cute哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,c…cute…哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也試穿下別的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有事想求你們幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是來穿COS服的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我說過不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不聽我說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉哦 太開心了不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想發送簡訊到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天…本來想送弄錯樂透6的賠禮來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說又用D-MAIL了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 等…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去發生了改變 使萌郁整個人都消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不想偷聽你們說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華君 你想發送怎樣的簡訊到過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想變成女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不大喜歡自己的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能變成女生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能多些自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 助手 看來你犯了一個決定性的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯誤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華子不是女生 是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是膚淺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是科學家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用自己的雙眼好好確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼可愛的孩子怎麼可能會是男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 冒犯一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是認真的 我真的想變成女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 僅靠發送D-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未必真的能改變性別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽過一個傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在懷孕期間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃肉的話 會生男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃蔬菜的話 就會生女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想發送D-MAIL 告訴你母親要多吃蔬菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我來實現你的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 琉華君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變性別是不是太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為這事靠吃點蔬菜就能辦成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是有科學依據的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是他煩惱的事而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣能讓他滿意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉華子 從今天開始你就是我們Lab的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Labmem No.006
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就趕快進行實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今年是17歲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說是1993出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機開始在日本普及是什麼時候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是1996年左右的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有簡訊功能時似乎還要更晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 在漆原出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他母親很有可能沒有手機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就發不了D-MAIL了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
