Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改造成能發射毒電波如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒電波有你們就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真好 再多罵我一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的才能真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有手機的話 發送到B.B.Call不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B.B.Call
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透過電波 向小型接收器發送信號的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於1990年代爆發性流行起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後因手機的普及而銷聲匿跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B.B.Call？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個東西我第一次見識到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:37.48,neta1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}Saleser
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:37.65,neta2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx75)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:37.48,neta3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}銷售經理。\N與celeb發音相似。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真清楚啊 不是名十七而是推銷員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那寫著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己讀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Labmem No.006 漆原琉華
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First Mission
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查你母親是否有B.B.Call
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後弄到號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.16,*Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽有B.B.Call
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮好簡訊的內容了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃一些蔬菜的話就能生下健康的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我聽說只能發送18個平假名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B.B.Call只能發送數字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個變換成數字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像濁音符號必須得用兩個數字來表示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能發送的只有半形36個文字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就超出了4個字元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:33.75,neta1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}此處變更
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:33.91,neta2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx87)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
