Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個變換成數字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.41,tip,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-5\fs28\bord0\be2\1c&H706D62&\pos(450,417)}多吃蔬菜的話就能生下健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了嗎 那就啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reading Steiner發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 也有這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這個很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這個絕對很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你盯著哪裡看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「琉華子是不是變成女孩子了」這種話很難問出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個平坦度…是失敗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我‧說‧你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一臉傻笑 到底在構思什麼樣的變態行為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭痛啊 真是不能對你們這對變態組合掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是變態啦 是變態紳士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣都好 真的是怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:02.46,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 桶子君不是變態是紳士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 世界線確實移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.50,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,你被他毒害了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…是什麼…
